# 🛒 Shopping Cart Using Arrays in JavaScript

## 📌 Description
This is a simple Shopping Cart web application built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.  
The project demonstrates how to manage cart items using arrays and dynamically update the UI using DOM manipulation.

---

## 🚀 Features
- ➕ Add items with name and price  
- 📦 Store items in a JavaScript array  
- 📋 Display items dynamically  
- ❌ Remove individual items  
- 🧹 Clear entire cart  
- 💰 Calculate total price automatically  

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- HTML5  
- CSS3  
- JavaScript (Arrays & DOM Manipulation)  

